Thraex, tampaknya dia mahal.

266
00:43:00,706 --> 00:43:02,666
- Selamat.
- Terima kasih.

267
00:43:03,917 --> 00:43:05,002
Luar biasa.

268
00:43:09,923 --> 00:43:11,383
Dari mana asalmu?

269
00:43:17,181 --> 00:43:18,182
Bicara.

270
00:43:21,602 --> 00:43:22,811
Kataku bicara.

271
00:43:22,895 --> 00:43:27,191
